  "description": "A close-up, top-down view of a vibrant red and yellow tulip in full bloom. The flower's petals curl outwards, revealing a dark, textured center with prominent stamens and pistil. The interior of the tulip transitions from a bright yellow near the base to a rich, deep red at the petal edges. The tulip is surrounded by partially visible green foliage and another, lighter-colored tulip petal. The background is dark and out of focus.",
